A cyberpunk-style illustration of a vast neon-lit cityscape at night where towering server buildings are connected by flowing streams of glowing data rivers in electric blue and magenta. In the foreground, a lone figure sits at a floating workstation, orchestrating dozens of holographic folder icons that spiral upward like a digital tornado, each folder pulsing with synchronized energy as streams of code flow down from the dark purple sky like rain. The folders appear to be drinking in the data streams, refreshing and glowing brighter. Flying drones carry packets of light between the structures. The atmosphere is moody with fog rolling through neon-lit alleyways below, reflecting off wet streets. The scene conveys automation, synchronization, and the satisfying rhythm of keeping many things perfectly updated at once.
